== 经济 ==
峇株巴辖县在《2030年柔佛州结构计划》（Rancangan Struktur Negeri Johor 2030）里被称作「生产与加工业核心」（Manufacturing & Processing Nucleus），并著重发展纺织与服装业、轻工业、家具制造业、电子与电气业、食品加工业，以及农业旅游。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jpbd.johor.gov.my/images/jpbd_muatturun/Bahan_DRSNJ2030/Ringkasan_Eksekutif_DRSNJ2030.pdf|title=Ringkasan Eksekutif DRSNJ 2030|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180407053538/http://jpbd.johor.gov.my/images/jpbd_muatturun/Bahan_DRSNJ2030/Ringkasan_Eksekutif_DRSNJ2030.pdf|archive-date=2018-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jpbd.johor.gov.my/images/jpbd_muatturun/Bahan_DRSNJ2030/Laporan_Draf_RSN_Johor2030.pdf|title=Laporan Draf Rancangan Struktur Negeri Johor 2030|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=Jabatan Perancangan Bandar dan Desa Negeri Johor|pages=6-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181104130106/https://jpbd.johor.gov.my/images/jpbd_muatturun/Bahan_DRSNJ2030/Laporan_Draf_RSN_Johor2030.pdf|archive-date=2018-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>
